Name Rascal/Libraries/Benchmark/systemTime

Function
  1. int systemTime()
  2. int systemTime(void () block)
Description
  1. Current system time in nanoseconds since the start of the thread that runs the code that calls this function.
  2. System time in nanoseconds needed to execute the code block.
